dct_title_s: Satsuma kokusei saikenzu: tsuketari ryakushi; Kashihara Yoshinaga seizu.
dct_description_sm: Copperplate print. Oriented with north to the left. Relief shown pictorially. Inset: Kagoshima no zu, 1:36,453. Includes distance chart, list of population and number of households, area geography, etc. 1 map: col.; 47 x 65 cm., folded to 18 x 10 cm.
